<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「ピンポーン」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">ユウキ</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi"><sentence>　「いらっしゃい、おじいちゃん、おばあちゃん。</sentence>
<sentence type="quasi">もう最後の日になっちゃったね」</sentence>
</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">おじい</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi"><sentence>　「なあ、ユウキ。</sentence>
<sentence type="quasi">夕べ帰ってから、おばあちゃんとも話してたんだが、囲碁っておもしろいなあ」</sentence>
</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">ユウキ</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi"><sentence>　「そうだね。</sentence>
<sentence>ボクもそう思ったよ。</sentence>
<sentence>早く打ちたくて、お父さんと打ったんだよ。</sentence>
<sentence type="quasi">そうしたらね、へへへ」</sentence>
</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">おばあ</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「勝ったの？」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">ユウキ</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi"><sentence>　「いつもハンデは<ruby rubyText="せい">星</ruby><ruby rubyText="もく">目</ruby>（９個）置いて勝ったり、負けたりなんだけど、きのうは圧勝だったんだよ！</sentence>
<sentence type="quasi">　お父さんの石を取っちゃったんだ」</sentence>
</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">おばあ</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「まあ、すごいわね」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">ユウキ</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi"><sentence>　「おばあちゃんが言ってたでしょ？</sentence>
<sentence>　相手の弱い石をつくるんだって。</sentence>
<sentence>自分が切られて困りそうならつなぐんだって。</sentence>
<sentence type="quasi">それでね、お父さんの白石をなるべく切って、ボクの弱い黒石を逃げながら囲っていったら、置いてきぼりになってた白石に目ができなくなっちゃったんだよ」</sentence>
</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">おじい</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi"><sentence>　「ほぉー。</sentence>
<sentence type="quasi">きのう習ったことがすぐ役立ったんだな」</sentence>
</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">ユウキ</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「そうなんだよ！」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">おばあ</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi"><sentence>　「それはよかった。</sentence>
<sentence type="quasi">私もうれしいわ」</sentence>
</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">おじい</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi"><sentence>　「ユウキの話を聞いてたら、ワシも楽しくなってきたぞ。</sentence>
<sentence type="quasi">さて、きょうはヨセのことを勉強するんだったな」</sentence>
</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">おばあ</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi"><sentence>　「そうね。</sentence>
<sentence>ところで、中盤戦のあとは終盤戦っていうんだけど、いったい中盤ってどこまでのことを言うのかしら。</sentence>
<sentence>ユウキはわかる？」</sentence>
</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">ユウキ</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi"><sentence>　「うーん。</sentence>
<sentence>中盤って、お互いに石を囲いあう戦いだよね。</sentence>
<sentence type="quasi">お互いに弱い石<sampling type="end" />がなくなっちゃうと、戦いも終わっちゃうよね」</sentence>
</sentence>
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
